text: Macht (also known as Macht (Gun Court Singles Series) or Macht / B.L.E.E.D) is an EP by Swedish noise rock band Brainbombs. It is apart of the 7" series "Gun Court Singles Series" by Wabana Ore Limited. On the EP, both songs are mono but on the Singles Collection they are stereo. == Track list == == References == Category:1998 albums Category:Brainbombs albums Category:Rock albums
